{
  "title": "Midnight Craving Aerated Dutch Soy Milk Bake",
  "description": "A low-calorie, briny, aerated Dutch dish featuring soy milk, perfect for a midnight craving. This wok-based recipe is a unique twist on traditional Dutch cuisine.",
